@page
@model             IndexModel

@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Index";
    Layout = "~/Pages/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container-fluid services py-5">
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="mx-auto text-center mb-5" style="max-width: 800px;">
            <p class="fs-4 text-uppercase text-center" style="color: #ffc0cb;">Spa Vui Ve</p>
            <h1 class="display-3">Chăm sóc sắc đẹp, chăm sóc tâm hồn</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="services-item bg-light border-4 border-end rounded p-4" style="border: 2px solid #ffc0cb;color: #ffc0cb;">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-8">
                            <div class="services-content text-end">
                                <h3>Câu hỏi 1</h3>
                                <p>Vào mỗi bữa sáng thức dậy, bạn thấy da mình như thế nào?</p>
                                <div class="row mb-3">
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">A. Tốt</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">B. Vẫn còn nhiều dầu</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">C. Khô và ráp</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">D. Mẫn đỏ</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <div class="services-img d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded">
                                <img src="~/images/question_1.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="services-item bg-light border-4 border-start rounded p-4" style="border: 2px solid #ffc0cb;color: #ffc0cb;">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <div class="services-img d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded">
                                <img src="~/images/question_2.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="">

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-8">
                            <div class="services-content text-start">
                                <h3>Câu hỏi 2</h3>
                                <p>Thực hiện rửa mặt với sữa rửa mặt của bạn với nước ấm. Từ 20 – 30′ sau, cảm nhận của da bạn là thế nào?</p>
                                <p>Lưu ý trong 20 – 30′ không sử dụng thêm bất kỳ mỹ phẩm nào nhé.</p>

                                <div class="row mb-3">
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">A. Bình thường, không có sự khác biệt so với trước lúc ngủ</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">B. Nhiều dầu. Tập trung ở mũi và trán</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">C. Khô và nẻ</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">D. Tẩy đỏ, bong da</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="services-item bg-light border-4 border-end rounded p-4" style="border: 2px solid #ffc0cb;color: #ffc0cb;">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-8">
                            <div class="services-content text-end">
                                <h3>Câu hỏi 3</h3>
                                <p>Hãy nhìn kỹ xem lỗ chân lông trên da bạn ra sao?</p>
                                <div class="row mb-3">
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">A. Tốt</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">B. Vẫn còn nhiều dầu</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">C. Khô và ráp</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">D. Mẫn đỏ</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <div class="services-img d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded">
                                <img src="~/images/question_3.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="services-item bg-light border-4 border-start rounded p-4" style="border: 2px solid #ffc0cb;color: #ffc0cb;">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <div class="services-img d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded">
                                <img src="~/images/question_4.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="">

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-8">
                            <div class="services-content text-start">
                                <h3>Câu hỏi 4</h3>
                                <p>Từ nào dưới đây có thể miêu tả kết cấu da bạn?</p>
                                <div class="row mb-3">
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">A. Mềm mịn</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">B. Nhiều dầu</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">C. Hơi khô</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">D. Mỏng, lộ đường mạch máu</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="services-item bg-light border-4 border-end rounded p-4" style="border: 2px solid #ffc0cb;color: #ffc0cb;">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-8">
                            <div class="services-content text-end">
                                <h3>Câu hỏi 5</h3>
                                <p>Vào buổi trưa, da bạn ở tình trạng nào? (Không dùng tay, chỉ soi gương để đoán)</p>
                                <div class="row mb-3">
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">A. Như buổi sáng</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">B. Sáng</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">C. Khô</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">D. Nhạy cảm </a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <div class="services-img d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded">
                                <img src="~/images/question_5.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="">

                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12">
                <div class="services-item bg-light border-4 border-start rounded p-4" style="border: 2px solid #ffc0cb;color: #ffc0cb;">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-4">
                            <div class="services-img d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center rounded">
                                <img src="~/images/question_6.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded" alt="">

                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-8">
                            <div class="services-content text-start">
                                <h3>Câu hỏi 6</h3>
                                <p>Bạn có thường xuyên nặn mụn trứng cá?</p>
                                <div class="row mb-3">
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">A. thỉnh thoảng</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">C. Không bao giờ</a>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-6 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">B. Thường xuyên, đặc biệt vào chu kỳ</a>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-2 px-4 mx-2  my-2" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">D. Chỉ khi tràn điểm</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-12 my-2">
            <div class="services-btn text-center">
                <a href="#" class="btn rounded-pill py-3 px-5" style="background-color: #ffc0cb; color: #333; border: 2px solid #ffc0cb; transition: all 0.3s ease;">Xem kết quả</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



